response.overview: There's no cover charge to get into this 1986 show at the world-famous Whisky A Go-Go, where glam gods Jetboy take the stage and rock the house to the enjoyment of the big-haired, lace- and leather-laden Sunset Strip faithful. In addition to the live performance, this release also includes interviews with each member of the band's 2007 lineup and a slide show that retraces the group's 20-plus-year journey.
response.title: Jetboy: The Glam Years Movie
